tafsir[21]{c,v,t}:
  51,31,"Annabi Ibraahiima maaki Malaa'i…ìe …ìen : ko hon…óum woni fii mon? E ko faanditi…óon?"
  51,32,"Malaa'ika'en jaabii mo wonnde : menen, Allah neli men e yim…ìe bom…ìe …ìen faggitotoo…ìe kuu…óe bon…óe."
  51,33,"Fii yo men accitu e ma…ì…ìe, kaa∆¥e iw…óe e loope ju…óaa…óe"
  51,34,"Maandiniraa…óe ka Joomi maa an Ibraahiima, wurtaa…óe e yawtoo…ìe keeri Allah …ìen, fantinoo…ìe yeddugol Mo ngol."
  51,35,"Men yaltini taho kala gom…óim…ìe wonunoo…ìe e saare yim…ìe Luutu …ìen, fii wata lepte bom…ìe …ìen hawru e ma…ì…ìe."
  51,36,"Men tawaano e nden saare, si wanaa suudu juul…ìe wooturu, ndun le ko suudu …ìeynguure Luutu nden (yo o his)."
  51,37,"men acci e nden saare yim…ìe Luutu, batteeji lepte …óen, ko holla wonnde …óe yanuno e ma…ì…ìe, wona waajitor…óum kala huloowo lepte muusu…óe …óen yanunoo…óe e ma…ì…ìe, ontigi hula wa…óugol sugu kuu…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen, fii da…óugol …óen lepte."
  51,38,"Men acci kadi maande e Muusaa, tuma nde Men nulunoo mo e Fir'awna, wonndude e hujjaaji …ìanngu…ói, wonannde kala huloowo e lepte muusu…óe …óen."
  51,39,"Kono Fir'awna …óuurni fawaade e cemmbe e konu makko fow salii goonga, o wi'i Muusaa : ko mbil…óotoo…óo yim…ìe maa hara feetu…óo."
  51,40,"Men nanngi mo kanko e koneeli makko …óin fow, Men weddii …ìe ka maayo, …ìe yoolii …ìe halkii, tawde Fir'awna ko feliraa…óo fennugol mo ngol nodditoo rewetee…óo."
  51,41,"Men acci kadi maande e 'Adi'en, yim…ìe Huudu …ìen, wonannde kala huloowo lepte muusu…óe …óen, tuma nde Men wurtunoo e ma…ì…ìe henndu ndu ardaa e to…ìo, ndu worgintaa le…ó…óe ndu aldaa kadi e barke."
  51,42,"Ndu accataa hay wonkii maa jawdi ekw e kon ko ndu arani, si wanaa ndu muncay fii mun, ndu wa…óta …óum wano rappunde sariinde."
  51,43,"Men wa…ói kadi maande e Samuuda'en, yim…ìe Annabi Saalih …ìen, wonannde kala huloowo lepte muusu…óe …óen, tuma nde …ìe wi'ananoo : awa dakmitoree nguurndam mon …óam, ado lajal mon gal timmude."
  51,44,"∆Åe townitanii yawmiroore Joomi ma…ì…ìe gom…óingol e …óoftagol Mo ngol, haacaango lepte ngon nanngi …ìe, tawi hi…ìe ∆¥eewa ko …óum jippotoo kon. Tawde …ìe kammbirano lepte …óen, bal…óe tati ado …óe jippaade."
  51,45,"∆Åe waawaano du√±ugol lepte …óen gaay e ma…ì…ìe, …ìe he…ìaano kadi feere faabeede."
  51,46,"Gom…óii kadi Men halkiriino yim…ìe Nuuhu …ìen ado …ìee jantaa…ìe …óoo, yoolagol. Pellet, …ìen ko yim…ìe yaltunoo…ìe e …óoftaare Allah, wa…ói si …ìe hanndi e lepte Makko …óen."
  51,47,"Kammu ngun, Men mahir ngu doole Amen, Men …óiggini …óum. Pellet, ko Men yaanoo…ìe cebe mammba."
  51,48,"Leydi ndin kan, Men weertiranndi ho…óoo…ìe …ìen, wano nda…ó…óundi ma…ì…ìe. Men mo∆¥∆¥ii weertan …ìe ndi."
  51,49,"E kala huunde, Men tagii noone …ói…ói: wano deyel e gorel, kammu e leydi, njodrndi e maayo; balajo'o on waajitoray gootaagu Allah tagu…óo …óin On, tesko…óon fii kattal Makko ngal."
  51,50,"Dogee lepte Allah …óen, yaccoron e mbarjaari Makko ndin, …óoftaare e anngal yeddugol Mo. Min, wonannde on onon …ìee yim…ìe, ko mi jertinoowo e lepte Makko …óen, …ìanngu…óo jertinol."
  51,51,"Wata on wa…óde e Allah rewetee…óo goo ko rewon. Min, wonannde on immorde ka Makko, ko mi …ìanngu…óo jertinol."